high_descs: Turn right, move to the island near the sponge.
Pick up the knife near the sponge.
Turn right, move to the island, between the two chairs.
Slice the tomato with the knife.
Turn right, move to in front of the stove.
Put the knife in the pan.
Turn right, move to the island, between the two chairs.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn right, move to in front of the stove.
Put the tomato in the pan.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Turn right, move to the island, opposite the two chairs.
Place pan on the island left of the salt.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with a slice of tomato onto the island.

high_descs: Turn around and walk beside the kitchen island, then turn to your left so that you are facing the kitchen island.
Pick up the knife to the right of the green and yellow sponge.
Turn to your right and go towards the door, then turn to your left and to the spot between the two chairs and turn to your left, facing the kitchen island.
Cut the tomato, on the kitchen island, in front of the wine bottle, into slices.
Turn to your right and walk to the end of the island, then make a left and walk to the stove.
Place the knife in the fry pan, on the left of the stove.
Turn to your right and walk to the wall, then make another right and go back to the sliced tomato, on the island.
Pick up a slice of the tomato on the island.
Turn to your right, go to the end of the island, turn left and go back to the stove.
Place the tomato slice into the fry pan on the left side of the stove, to the right of the knife.
Pick up the fry pan with the knife and potato inside it.
Turn around and walk to the middle of the kitchen Island.
Place the fry pan on the island , close to the left , center edge.
anns.task_desc: Put a fry pan containing a knife and tomato slice on the kitchen island.

high_descs: Step to the right and face the end of the kitchen table.
Pick up the knife on the kitchen table.
Walk around to the right side of the table and face it.
Cut the tomato sitting on the kitchen table.
Walk around the right side of the table and walk forward to face the stove on the right.
Place the knife on the pan on the front left burner.
Turn right and walk across the room and then turn around and walk forward and to the left to face the kitchen table.
Pick up a slice of the tomato on the kitchen table.
Walk around the right side of the table and walk forward to face the stove on the right.
Place the tomato slice on the pan on the front left burner.
Pick up the pan with the tomato and knife in it.
Turn around and walk forward to face the kitchen table.
Place the pan containing the knife and tomato slice on the end of the kitchen table closest to the stove.
anns.task_desc: To Cut a tomato slice plus place the slice as well as the knife in a pan as well as moving the pan to the kitchen table.
